E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1437','7','县政府办','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">嘉政办发<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">[2012]30</span>号<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">各镇人民政府，县政府各部门，嘉鱼经济开发区管委会：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">为进一步完善全县新型农村合作医疗（以下简称新农合）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">制度，提高农村居民医疗保障水平，根据省卫生厅、省财政厅<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">《关于印发〈湖北省<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年新农合统筹补偿方案指导意见〉的通知》（鄂卫发<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">[2012]8</span>号）精神，经县人民政府同意，现就完善新型农村合作医疗补偿方案有关事项通知如下：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">一、提高筹资水平，增加财政补助<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2012</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">年起，财政对新农合的补助标准从每人每年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">200</span>元提高到每人每年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">240</span>元，其中，中央财政每人每年补助标准由<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">108</span>元提高到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">132</span>元，省财政每人每年补助标准由<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">64.2</span>元提高到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">73.8</span>元，县财政每人每年补助标准由<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">27.8</span>元提高到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">34.2</span>元；农民个人缴费标准由每人每年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">30</span>元提高到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">50</span>元，筹资总额为每人每年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">290</span>元。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">五保户、低保户、特困优抚参合对象个人缴费部分由财政部门、民政部门审核后从五保转移支付经费、医疗救助资金和优抚经费中解决。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">二、合理调整补偿方案，明显提高保障水平<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（一）基金补偿范围与分配<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1.</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">基金补偿范围<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">新农合基金（含利息）只能用于参合农村居民符合规定的医药费用的补偿，不得用于经办机构工作经费或购买商业医疗保险。同时，以下项目不纳入补偿范围：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑴超出新农合报销药品目录、基本诊疗项目和医疗服务设施范围目录发生的医疗费用；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑵斗殴致伤、自杀、自残、服毒、吸毒、工伤、酗酒、整容、整形、美容、矫形、交通肇事、计划生育、职业病发生的医疗费用，以及其他涉及第三方责任人的医疗费用（如替人打工负伤，高空坠物造成伤害等同类型事件）；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑶经鉴定属医疗事故或已经发生医疗事故争议尚未经过鉴定的医疗费用；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑷自点药品和医学检查的费用，与疾病无关的检查、治疗费用和不符合处方用药的药品费用（排除性的诊断检查费用除外）；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑸应由公共卫生项目负担和国家、省已有补助政策的疾病救治费用；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑹境外就医发生的医疗费用；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑺各种科研性、临床验证性的诊疗项目费用；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑻违反国家法律和政策以及其他有关规定的。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2.</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">基金分配<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">新农合基金分为住院基金、门诊基金、风险基金三类，其中住院基金为人平<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">230</span>元，用于参加新型农村合作医疗病人封顶线以内的住院医疗费用的补偿。门诊统筹基金为人平<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">55</span>元，分为一般门诊医疗费用补偿基金和门诊慢性病（大病）治疗费用补偿基金。一般门诊医疗费用补偿基金为人平<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">50</span>元，分镇独立核算，用于一般门诊医疗费用补偿；门诊慢性病（大病）治疗费用补偿基金为人平<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>元，用于恶性肿瘤、高血压Ⅲ级、中风后遗症、冠心病、重症糖尿病、肾移植抗排、白血病等慢性病（大病）患者门诊治疗费用的限额补偿。风险基金为人平<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>元，用于弥补新型农村合作医疗基金非正常超支的临时周转困难。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（二）补偿标准<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1.</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">门诊补偿：新农合门诊补偿全部采用门诊统筹管理模式，分为一般门诊补偿和门诊慢性病（大病）门诊补偿两种。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>）一般门诊补偿：参加新农合农村居民的门诊就医以镇、村两级定点医疗机构为主，每次就医发生的门诊医药费用新农合补偿比例为<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">40%</span>。同时，每次就医门诊补偿封顶线村卫生室为<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">13</span>元，镇卫生院为<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">17</span>元，个人年度累计门诊补偿封顶线为<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">260</span>元，按规定比例支付的一般诊疗费纳入上述封顶线计算。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>）门诊慢性病（大病）补偿：具体方案另行制订。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2.</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">住院补偿<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">住院医疗费用补偿设立起付线和封顶线，起付线标准为：镇级定点医疗机构<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100</span>元，县级定点医疗机构<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">300</span>元，市级定点医疗机构<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1000</span>元，省级定点医疗机构<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1200</span>元。封顶线标准为<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>万元，即新型农村合作医疗基金为每个人在<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>年内累计补偿住院医疗费用总额不超过<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>万元。对参合农民在一年内患同一种疾病连续转院治疗的，只计算其中最高级别医院的一次起付线。五保户、低保户、特困优抚参合对象不设起付线。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">参加新型农村合作医疗的农民每次住院的医疗费用在起付线以下部分由个人负担，超过起付线以上部分的医疗费用从新型农村合作医疗住院基金中按比例补偿：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（一）在镇级定点医疗机构诊治的住院费用政策范围内补偿比例为：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、住院费用<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">101</span>元以上部分，按<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">85%</span>比例补偿。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（二）在县级定点医疗机构诊治的住院费用政策范围内补偿比例为：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-